Start from here!

#Install gcc minGW compiler in your machine. Download it from here https://osdn.net/projects/mingw/releases/
#install xampp with latest php version and apache web server . This project has tested using php 7.2.1 on xampp apache
#put the source files in your root directory . Typically "htdocs" under "xampp" folder of your "XAMPP" installation path
#Start the apache from your xampp control panel
#Jump to the browser and type "http://localhost"
------------------------------That's all--------------